trans-unit.source: Provides location mapping support for script resources.
A <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping> object can contain a collection of mappings to script resources, such as a script file (.js).
Each item in the collection maps to a <xref:System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition> object by using either a name or name/assembly pair.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping"></xref> class.
Adds a <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition"></xref> object to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping"></xref> object.
The name of the script resource.
A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition"></xref> object that specifies location support for script resources.
Adds a <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition"></xref> object to the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping"></xref> object.

An <xref href="System.Reflection.Assembly"></xref> object that contains the script resource.
A <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition"></xref> object that specifies location support for script resources.
Removes all <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceDefinition"></xref> objects from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ScriptResourceMapping"></xref> object.
Returns the specified object from the object based on the name parameter.
